      "text": "The Original Problem: \nComputer memory is just bytes. \nHow do you store different kinds of things?",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The Original Problem: \nComputer memory is just bytes. \nHow do you store different kinds of things?",
